                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "As a civilian who knew little of mercenary life, Sania once though: \"The more one invests in the early stages, the better their equipment, the more Mora they'll earn, and better they can improve economic conditions at home.\" As such, she asked around, and was shocked to learn that a certain group of outlander soldiers were the best equipped in the land...",
